{"tid":2432803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特區政府：本港經濟自由、司法獨立  堅決反對美國傳統基金會的說法","createTime":"2021-03-04T14:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T15:51:45.000Z","uid":227801,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"f6d9e381aec55571a06802115d35bf89a16284da","tid":2432803,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:27:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=426201\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426201&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv3fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=96111c45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426201&h=4b61cfab\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=426201</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】特區政府對美國傳統基金會將香港剔出經濟自由度指數評級表示極度失望，指有關決定既無必要，亦無道理。<br />\n<br />\n政府發表聲明，堅決反對基金會指本港經濟政策最終由北京控制的說法，指基金會突然將香港剔出評級是政治上的偏見，亦偏離基金會的慣常做法。<br />\n<br />\n聲明強調，基本法列明本港對經濟及貿易政策享有高度自主，在經濟自由、司法獨立下，香港將會保持開放、安全及多元的國際金融中心，基金會的決定忽略了在基本法下，特區享有獨立的關稅區及作為世貿組織成員的因素。"},{"pid":"f72059d5d6b2201cf7cb73f72ea7990c17916532","tid":2432803,"uid":227801,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:29:19.000Z","msg":"司法獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2ea120c2e72f4f8aa3fb434a1df9b9bc159601","tid":2432803,"uid":19513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:30:33.000Z","msg":"腐乳"},{"pid":"80be461122e5a1ef5c6e29bf5ee056da23821b30","tid":2432803,"uid":105176,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:30:42.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你係中國呀 咪扮啦"},{"pid":"42bd30067830e0c3e820c2f4acc074829c7ca865","tid":2432803,"uid":323876,"like":0,"di